questions.quote: Oh, ain't this nice? It's so quiet, I could just lie here all day.
Well, the first time didn't really count... I mean, y'know, 's'Barry.
Whoa, wait, Pheebs, wait a second! Don't you wanna stay here and talk about it?
Clearly I did not start drinking enough at the start of the meal.
Yes! Remember? Right before we cut the cake, I went up to you and I said...
Ah, y-y-you're sure you don't want me to do it again? I could do it with an accent, you know, Southern "I could go right now, maaan!"
Yeah. Sorry about that. Oh, hey little girl. Uhh, is-is your mommy, or sister, or babysitter by any chance a hot girl?
Okay, see, see, you guys, what if we don't get magic beans? I mean, what if all we've got are.. beans?
I know, I know I really like you too. But we-we can't date. It's against the rules. It's forbidden.
Well, uh, let's try one more. . . there you go, say Ernie's, 8 o'clock.
